### Sprint 1 — Frontend Scaffold

#### [NEW] Next.js 14 project in `e:\CRTAIS\frontend\`
Initialized via `npx -y create-next-app@14 ./` with TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, App Router, ESLint.

#### [NEW] [page.tsx](file:///e:/CRTAIS/frontend/app/page.tsx)
Landing dashboard with:
- Hero section introducing CRTAIS
- Quick-action cards (New Site Intake, View Map, Browse Rules)
- Premium dark theme with glassmorphism cards, gradient accents, smooth animations

#### [NEW] [layout.tsx](file:///e:/CRTAIS/frontend/app/layout.tsx)
Root layout with:
- Google Font (Inter)
- Global navigation sidebar (collapsible)
- Dark mode by default

#### [NEW] [page.tsx](file:///e:/CRTAIS/frontend/app/site-intake/page.tsx)
Site intake form page:
- Coordinate input (lat/lng) with map pin drop
- Plot polygon upload (GeoJSON file) or draw-on-map
- Climate zone auto-detection
- Building typology selector
- Submit → POST to FastAPI `/api/sites`

#### [NEW] Components in `frontend/components/`
- `Sidebar.tsx` — navigation sidebar
- `SiteIntakeForm.tsx` — the intake form component
- `MapPicker.tsx` — Leaflet map for pin drop / polygon draw

