### Sprint 1 — Backend Scaffold

#### [NEW] FastAPI project in `e:\CRTAIS\backend\`

#### [NEW] [main.py](file:///e:/CRTAIS/backend/app/main.py)
FastAPI application with CORS middleware, router registration, startup event for DB connections.

#### [NEW] [config.py](file:///e:/CRTAIS/backend/app/config.py)
Pydantic Settings for PostgreSQL DSN, MongoDB URI, and other env vars.

#### [NEW] [sites.py](file:///e:/CRTAIS/backend/app/routers/sites.py)
REST endpoints:
- `POST /api/sites` — create a new site (stores geometry in PostGIS)
- `GET /api/sites` — list all sites
- `GET /api/sites/{id}` — get site detail with geometry
- `DELETE /api/sites/{id}` — remove a site

#### [NEW] [health.py](file:///e:/CRTAIS/backend/app/routers/health.py)
`GET /api/health` — returns DB connection status.

#### [NEW] [site.py](file:///e:/CRTAIS/backend/app/models/site.py)
SQLAlchemy model with GeoAlchemy2 geometry column for plot polygon storage.

#### [NEW] [site_schema.py](file:///e:/CRTAIS/backend/app/schemas/site_schema.py)
Pydantic schemas for site create/read operations with GeoJSON geometry support.

#### [NEW] [postgres.py](file:///e:/CRTAIS/backend/app/db/postgres.py)
Async SQLAlchemy engine + session factory for PostGIS.

#### [NEW] [mongo.py](file:///e:/CRTAIS/backend/app/db/mongo.py)
Motor (async MongoDB driver) client setup.

#### [NEW] [requirements.txt](file:///e:/CRTAIS/backend/requirements.txt)
Dependencies: `fastapi`, `uvicorn`, `sqlalchemy`, `geoalchemy2`, `asyncpg`, `motor`, `pydantic-settings`, `python-dotenv`, `alembic`.

#### [NEW] [.env.example](file:///e:/CRTAIS/backend/.env.example)
Template environment variables.

